ally stabbed with a knife in Daliyat al-Karmel. A suspect was arrested in the case. The prosecution later canceled the charge of premeditated murder and replaced it with manslaughter only, due to alleged failures in the police investigation.","review_status":"auto","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2021-01-01_2021-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2021-01-01_2021-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":842}